name: PokePricer
0:
”Alexa, open Poke Pricer”
”How much is Tapu Lele GX?”
”Search for Pikachu”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: poke pricer
des:
No more fumbling with your phone, or typing tediously on your computer. Now you can find the price of any Pokemon card in standard rotation!

Prices are always up to date and searching for a card couldn't be easier. Poke Pricer will always return a relevant response. No more wondering how much a card is worth, find out now!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
